---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import PrimaryButton from "../../components/PrimaryButton.astro";
---

<Layout title="Admin Management | UU MEMO">
    <Header />

    <main
        class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20 min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col w-full self-stretch"
    >
        <!-- Auth Loading -->
        <div
            id="auth-loading"
            class="fixed inset-0 z-[60] bg-uu-base flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 transition-opacity duration-300"
        >
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 border-4 border-uu-sub border-t-uu-main rounded-full animate-spin"
            >
            </div>
            <p
                class="text-uu-main/60 tracking-widest text-sm font-medium uppercase"
            >
                Authenticating...
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Admin Login UI (Intermediate Page) -->
        <div
            id="admin-login-ui"
            class="hidden fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-uu-base flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6"
        >
            <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-12 shadow-2xl border border-uu-sub/20 text-center space-y-10 animate-in fade-in zoom-in duration-700">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-uu-main/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto border-4 border-white shadow-sm">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-uu-main text-4xl">admin_panel_settings</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-uu-dark font-logo uppercase tracking-wider">Restricted Access</h2>
                    <p class="text-sm text-uu-main/60 leading-relaxed">This area is reserved for administrators only. Please sign in with an authorized Google account to continue.</p>
                </div>

                <div id="unauthorized-msg" class="hidden p-4 bg-uu-sub/10 rounded-xl border border-uu-sub/20">
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-uu-main/60 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Access Denied</p>
                    <p id="denied-email" class="text-xs text-uu-main/40 font-mono italic mb-3"></p>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-uu-main/40 leading-tight">Please ensure your email is granted permission in Firestore rules.</p>
                </div>

                <button
                    id="admin-login-btn"
                    class="w-full py-5 bg-uu-dark text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-4 font-black tracking-[0.3em] uppercase hover:bg-uu-main hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-uu-main/20 transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-lg shadow-uu-dark/10 group"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform">login</span>
                    Sign in with Google
                </button>

                <p class="text-[10px] text-uu-main/30 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Authorized Personnel Only</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Admin Dashboard Container (Exact Mirror of User Dashboard Layout) -->
        <div
            id="admin-dashboard"
            class="hidden opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 dashboard-layout w-full"
        >
            <!-- LEFT COLUMN: Sidebar -->
            <aside class="dashboard-sidebar">
                <div
                    class="bg-uu-light p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-uu-sub/30 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center text-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-20 h-20 bg-uu-main/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-4 border-white shadow-sm mb-4 shrink-0"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-uu-main text-4xl"
                            >admin_panel_settings</span
                        >
                    </div>

                    <div class="w-full">
                        <h1
                            class="text-lg font-bold font-logo text-uu-dark mb-0.5 truncate px-2"
                        >
                            ADMINISTRATOR
                        </h1>
                        <p
                            id="admin-email"
                            class="text-[10px] text-uu-main/60 tracking-wider font-mono truncate px-2"
                        >
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-uu-sub/20 rounded-full my-6 shrink-0"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <nav class="w-full flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                        <button
                            class="tab-btn active group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all w-full bg-uu-main text-white shadow-md text-left active:scale-[0.98]"
                            data-tab="editor"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >edit_note</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >文章編輯</span
                            >
                        </button>
                        <button
                            class="tab-btn group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all w-full text-uu-main/50 hover:bg-uu-sub/10 hover:text-uu-main text-left active:scale-[0.98]"
                            data-tab="posts"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >inventory_2</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >文章管理</span
                            >
                        </button>
                        <button
                            class="tab-btn group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all w-full text-uu-main/50 hover:bg-uu-sub/10 hover:text-uu-main text-left active:scale-[0.98]"
                            data-tab="draft"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >auto_fix</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >草稿工具</span
                            >
                        </button>
                        <button
                            class="tab-btn group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all w-full text-uu-main/50 hover:bg-uu-sub/10 hover:text-uu-main text-left active:scale-[0.98]"
                            data-tab="comments"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >forum</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >留言管理</span
                            >
                        </button>
                        <button
                            class="tab-btn group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all w-full text-uu-main/50 hover:bg-uu-sub/10 hover:text-uu-main text-left active:scale-[0.98]"
                            data-tab="author"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >person_edit</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >作者設定</span
                            >
                        </button>
                        <button
                            class="tab-btn group flex items-center gap-4 px-5 py-4 rounded-2xl transition-all w-full text-uu-main/50 hover:bg-uu-sub/10 hover:text-uu-main text-left active:scale-[0.98]"
                            data-tab="system"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >tune</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >全站設定</span
                            >
                        </button>

                        <div class="h-2"></div>

                        <button
                            id="logout-btn"
                            class="w-full flex items-center gap-3.5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-uu-main/40 hover:text-uu-main hover:bg-uu-sub/10 transition-all group border border-transparent hover:border-uu-sub/20 text-left mt-2 cursor-pointer"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl"
                                >logout</span
                            >
                            <span
                                class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest leading-none"
                                >登出</span
                            >
                        </button>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: Content -->
            <div
                class="dashboard-content bg-uu-light rounded-[2.5rem] border border-uu-sub/30 shadow-sm min-h-[700px] flex flex-col overflow-hidden"
            >
                <!-- CONTENT: EDITOR -->
                <section
                    id="tab-editor"
                    class="tab-content w-full flex-1 flex flex-col p-10"
                >
                    <div
                        class="flex items-center gap-3.5 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-uu-sub/20"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-uu-sub/10 flex items-center justify-center text-uu-main"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                                >description</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-uu-dark">內容創作</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-8 flex-1">

                        <!-- Top Meta -->
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label
                                    class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest"
                                    >Article Slug</label
                                >
                                <input
                                    id="post-slug"
                                    type="text"
                                    class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm"
                                    placeholder="例如: 2024-spring-trip"
                                />
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label
                                    class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest"
                                    >Visibility</label
                                >
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <select
                                        id="post-status"
                                        class="w-full appearance-none bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all cursor-pointer pr-10"
                                    >
                                        <option value="public"
                                            >立即發佈 (Public)</option
                                        >
                                        <option value="private"
                                            >私密閱讀 (Private)</option
                                        >
                                    </select>
                                    <span
                                        class="material-symbols-outlined absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-uu-main/40 pointer-events-none"
                                        >expand_more</span
                                    >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Markdown Upload Dropzone -->
                        <div
                            id="md-dropzone"
                            class="border-2 border-dashed border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl py-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-colors hover:border-uu-main/50 hover:bg-uu-sub/5 group cursor-pointer"
                        >
                            <input
                                type="file"
                                id="md-file-input"
                                accept=".md"
                                class="hidden"
                            />
                            <span
                                class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-uu-main/30 group-hover:text-uu-main transition-colors"
                                >cloud_upload</span
                            >
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-uu-main/60">
                                    拖移 .md 檔案至此，或點擊選擇
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-[10px] text-uu-main/30 mt-1 italic"
                                >
                                    系統將自動讀取內容並嘗試生成 Slug
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Editor -->
                        <div class="space-y-2 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                            <label
                                class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest"
                                >Markdown Editor</label
                            >
                            <textarea
                                id="md-content"
                                class="w-full flex-1 min-h-[500px] bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-3xl p-8 text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed focus:outline-none focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-inner"
                                placeholder="# 標題..."></textarea>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Image Workshop -->
                        <div class="space-y-6 pt-6 border-t border-uu-sub/20">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <span
                                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-uu-main"
                                        >image</span
                                    >
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-uu-dark">
                                        影像工坊
                                    </h4>
                                </div>
                                <input
                                    type="file"
                                    id="image-input"
                                    multiple
                                    accept="image/*"
                                    class="hidden"
                                />
                                <button
                                    onclick="document.getElementById('image-input').click()"
                                    class="px-4 py-2 bg-uu-sub/10 text-uu-main hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white rounded-lg text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest uppercase transition-all active:scale-95"
                                    >批次上傳照片</button
                                >
                            </div>

                            <div
                                id="image-queue"
                                class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4"
                            >
                                <!-- Dynamic Preview Cards -->
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-8">
                            <PrimaryButton 
                                id="final-push-btn" 
                                text="SYNC TO GITHUB" 
                                icon="send"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- CONTENT: DRAFT TOOL -->
                <section id="tab-draft" class="tab-content hidden w-full flex-1 flex flex-col p-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3.5 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-uu-sub/20">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-uu-sub/10 flex items-center justify-center text-uu-main">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">auto_fix</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-uu-dark">文章草稿工具</h3>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-8 flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-4 no-scrollbar">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">1. 文章暫定標題或主題方向</label>
                                <input id="draft-q1" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="請在此填寫">
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">2. 目標受眾（這篇文章寫給誰看）</label>
                                <input id="draft-q2" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="請在此填寫">
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">3. 核心觀點與目的</label>
                                <input id="draft-q3" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="讀完這篇文章，讀者能帶走什麼？">
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">4. 關鍵段落與大綱（列出 3-5 個重點）</label>
                                <textarea id="draft-q4" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-3xl p-6 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all min-h-[120px] shadow-inner" placeholder="- 重點 1：&#10;- 重點 2：&#10;- 重點 3："></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">5. 個人獨特經驗與細節（文章的靈魂）</label>
                                <textarea id="draft-q5" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-3xl p-6 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all min-h-[150px] shadow-inner" placeholder="請在此填寫你想放入的具體細節"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">6. 行文語氣與風格</label>
                                <input id="draft-q6" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="預設：輕鬆幽默的個人隨筆">
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">7. 必用語句或重點風格提示 (Optional)</label>
                                <textarea id="draft-q7" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-3xl p-6 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all min-h-[100px] shadow-inner" placeholder="如果有特定的口頭禪、關鍵詞，或希望模仿的特定風格，請在此填寫 (例如：文橫排版、多用分號...)"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">文章短網址 (Slug)</label>
                                    <input id="draft-slug" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="例如: 2024-trip">
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">分類 (Category)</label>
                                    <input id="draft-cat" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="例如：生活隨筆">
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-2">
                                    <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">標籤 (Tags)</label>
                                    <input id="draft-tags" type="text" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm" placeholder="用逗號分隔">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-2 mt-6 p-6 bg-uu-main/5 rounded-2xl border border-uu-main/10 shadow-inner">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">settings_suggest</span>
                                    進階：編輯預設指令模板 (Prompt Template)
                                </label>
                                <button
                                    id="save-template-btn"
                                    class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-1.5 bg-white border border-uu-sub/30 text-uu-main/60 rounded-xl text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white hover:border-uu-main transition-all shadow-sm active:scale-95"
                                >
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xs">cloud_upload</span>
                                    儲存到資料庫
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <textarea id="draft-template" class="w-full bg-uu-base/10 border border-uu-sub/30 rounded-3xl p-8 text-[11px] focus:outline-none focus:border-uu-main focus:bg-white transition-all min-h-[400px] font-mono leading-relaxed shadow-inner" placeholder="在這裡設定你的 Prompt 骨架..."># Role: 部落格作家與內容策略師

請根據我下方提供的【文章草稿表單】資訊，為我撰寫一篇結構完整、引人入勝且具備個人觀點的部落格文章。

## 📥 【文章草稿表單】（User Input）

1. **文章暫定標題或主題方向：** &#123;&#123;q1&#125;&#125;
2. **目標受眾（這篇文章寫給誰看）：** &#123;&#123;q2&#125;&#125;
3. **核心觀點與目的（讀完這篇文章，讀者能帶走什麼？）：** &#123;&#123;q3&#125;&#125;
4. **關鍵段落與大綱（列出 3-5 個重點）：**
&#123;&#123;q4&#125;&#125;
5. **個人獨特經驗與細節（必填，這是文章的靈魂）：**
   &#123;&#123;q5&#125;&#125;
6. **行文語氣與風格：**
   &#123;&#123;q6&#125;&#125;
7. **必用語句或風格提示：**
   &#123;&#123;q7&#125;&#125;

---

## 📤 輸出要求 (Output Requirements)

請分段為我產出以下三個區塊內容：

### 第一部分：Meta Data (YAML)
請直接產出 .md 的 Frontmatter 區塊：
```markdown
---
title: "【&#123;&#123;cat&#125;&#125;】幫我想一個吸睛的主題標題"
description: "請根據文章內容生成約 50 字的溫暖 SEO 摘要"
publishDate: &#123;&#123;date&#125;&#125;
category: [&#123;&#123;cat&#125;&#125;]
tags: [&#123;&#123;tags&#125;&#125;]
heroImage: '/images/&#123;&#123;datePath&#125;&#125;/&#123;&#123;datePath&#125;&#125;-&#123;&#123;slug&#125;&#125;-01.jpg'
---
```

### 第二部分：文章正文 (Markdown)
請嚴格遵守以下規則撰寫文章：
1. **Markdown 格式**：請使用標準 Markdown 語法（包含 H2 ##、H3 ### 標題、粗體、條列式清單、引用區塊等）。
2. **吸引人的開場**：第一段必須點出痛點或引起共鳴，直接破題。
3. **無縫融入細節**：將表單第 5 點的「經驗」與第 7 點的「必用語句」自然融合，增加「人味」。
4. **有力量的結尾**：總結觀點並提供 Call to Action。

### 第三部分：配圖建議與關鍵字
針對本文內容，請提供 3-5 個適合的配圖場景描述，並附上 DALL-E 或攝影關鍵字。</textarea>
                            <p class="text-[9px] text-uu-main/40 mt-1">您可以使用 <code class="bg-white px-1 py-0.5 rounded shadow-sm border border-uu-sub/10 opacity-80">&#123;&#123;變數&#125;&#125;</code> 來替換上方表單內容，例如：&#123;&#123;q1&#125;&#125;, &#123;&#123;cat&#125;&#125;, &#123;&#123;tags&#125;&#125;, &#123;&#123;q7&#125;&#125;</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-6">
                            <PrimaryButton id="generate-draft-btn" text="生成文章草稿 PROMPT" icon="temp_preferences_custom" />
                        </div>

                        <div id="draft-result-container" class="hidden space-y-4 animate-fade-in pb-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <label class="text-[10px] font-black text-uu-main/40 uppercase tracking-widest">生成的 AI PROMPT</label>
                                <button
